BipolarNRZ

BiPolar Non-Return to Zero Line Coding Technique

Calling Sequence

[Bipolar_out] = BipolarNRZ(x)

Parameters

x: Digital information signal
Bipolar_out: Bipolar NRZ output

Description

BipolarNRZ -It generates polar NRZ line coded output for the given input data x.

Examples

x =[1,1,0,0,0,1,1,0];//digital information signal
Bipolar_out = BipolarNRZ(x);
plot2d2(Bipolar_out);
disp(Bipolar_out);


